Version 0.2.0 (2017-07-17)
--------------------------

Bug Fixes
~~~~~~~~~

* **providers.beaker:** fix for an unkown status that was not being analyzed
* **providers.beaker:** fixing incorrect Exception & adding info if caught
* **providers.openshift:** infinite Loop Possible Waiting for Builds/Pods
* **provisioner.beaker:** fix transfer of ssh key
* **provisioners.beaker:** bug fix for validation and Beaker XML gen
* check for asset and beaker credential keys before performing operation on
* cleanup docker containers on failures of beaker provisioning
* create directory if beaker assets are within folder
* provider name must be a property


Features
~~~~~~~~

* **provisioners.beaker:** return Beaker Data
* **resources.host:** add metadata key to host profile
* add property to retrieve <provider>_name
* adding ip_address attribute for host objects
* get assets list for credentials
* ignore exception if asset folder already exist
* **resources.host:** host resource to accept ansible parameters
* **carbon:** ability to declare provider credentials in carbon configuration file" into develop


Chores
~~~~~~

* remove flask dependency and add pbr
* add line break when creating ssh public key
* accept versions with alphanimeric


Tests
~~~~~

* **carbon.test:** removal of invalid integration tests
* **carbon.provisioners**: create a Jenkins job to run nightly tests w/ provisioners x providers matrix


Documentation
~~~~~~~~~~~~~

* document ansible_params key available to hosts
* document metadata key for host resources
* update version number to match other carbon projects
* make the changelog show on the main documentation page


